{"tid":2130393,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"頭先食環去我鋪頭話員工唔準睇電視 笑死","createTime":"2020-07-29T07:36:26.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-29T07:55:53.000Z","uid":12034,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"c7e8bb58c3a48bb87b7695bea52545f6a26b824c","tid":2130393,"uid":12034,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T07:36:26.000Z","msg":"岩岩睇鋪打黎 問我關唔關電視<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我問佢乜撚野? 佢話食環黎巡 <br />\n<br />\n講員工食飯係得 但食飯時/無客睇電視當非進食 聚集<br />\n<br />\n下次唔警告 直接票控<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 笑到我仆街"},{"pid":"fa4d48570617864c4f60dd55ef71185346f7b6f6","tid":2130393,"uid":32722,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T07:37:17.000Z","msg":"咁撚好笑？"},{"pid":"553d08c770ed9db95e2ca0bbd8a801bf15e213bb","tid":2130393,"uid":73381,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T07:37:52.000Z","msg":"我叫左去買個白汁 咁d飯有d雞皇 就$26蚊<br />\n<br />\n條友問我要唔要加飲野黎飲 我唔洗講啦 就要百事 點知佢話百事有可樂<br />\n<br />\n我都唔知佢up咩鳩 跟住我話唔要野飲 佢話30蚊 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我話唔要 跟住佢話我係咪睇電視<br />\n<br />\n屌佢老味<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> on99<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3cba932ea0fa440bce98f5bb9f8d64cd3703308c","tid":2130393,"uid":32722,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T07:39:00.000Z","msg":"是咪黃店？"},{"pid":"620d9fb2b69b5240132b39dc71216f3c84ed4c3e","tid":2130393,"uid":15477,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T07:39:37.000Z","msg":"睇撚咗5分鐘先睇得明<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"84923288cf873fb78769